             ®| ®®®®| ®| ®®®®|  ®®®®| ®®®®| @{" Installation " LINK INST}
             ®|______________   ___®| ___®| @{" Instructions " LINK INSU}
             ®®®®®®®®®®®®®®®®|  ®®®®| ®®®®| @{" Future       " LINK FUTU}


      Welcome to LoTo99, a new lottery predictor and checker program,
      with features that include, a compact and well designed GUI and
      the ability to generate numbers using different methods.

      This verion also has support for the Thunderball game.

      Although LoTo99 is new, the idea came from one of my previous
      programs called Lotto-P&C. Lotto-P&C has been around for a few
      years now, it has been rewritten in three different computer
      languages and was designed to use a command line interface. In
      recent years though, the CLI has become less used and so I
      decided rewrite it in ACE Basic and add a GUI.

      LoTo99 basically does three things, it generates random numbers,
      stores them and checks them with the most recient draw. If thats
      what you need, then LoTo98 is the predictor and checker for you.

