    Over the next couple of months LoTo99 will be improved in
    the following ways:

    · The executable will become smaller and faster;
    · There will be more number generation methods;
    · I will update the CLI version and include it;
    · Added compatibility with lotteries in other countries.

    All of the above can only be improved if you write to @{"me" LINK INFO} with
